node.accessibility_caption: Photo by DeWayne Colley on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and outdoors.

node.text: Most entertainers get a big deal or movie before their life change! But all I had was God and he has been more than enough. I see people in the industry give their whole life to Hollywood waiting on the opportunity that they might get. But I always knew God was bigger than Hollywood. So I waited on God and he has not let me down. So the moral of the story is whoever you have your trust in controls you. So I’m just going to keep my trust in God. He’s already pushed me pass 90% of Hollywood anyway! #God #Jesusispoppin #Jesusbeenpoppin #kountrywayne #letthatsizzleinyourspirit #helpisontheway #love
